title: No honeymoon just yet for newly wed royal couple
text:
No honeymoon just yet for newly wed royal couple 7:38pm IST - 02:04
The new Duke and Duchess of Sussex plan to hit the ground running as a royal couple. They won't be taking a honeymoon yet, and will get stuck into their first royal engagement just days after Saturday's lavish wedding. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
